eventDetails.eventItemValue: Verify that the uplink ports used by the uplink set are enabled, linked, and correctly configured. Verify that both the LAG configuration and status on the upstream switch ports are correct. If the uplink set contains FCoE network(s), verify that the uplink port DCBX status and FCoE configuration on the upstream switch ports are correct or if the quality of service is configured as RoCE lossless then verify that the uplink port DCBX status and RoCE configuration on the upstream switch ports are correct.
